wiki.text:
The term 'eaglet' can refer to:

;Animals
* An eaglet, the immature young of an eagle, which in turn encompasses several
  species of bird of prey

;Ships
* HMS ''Eaglet'' (shore establishment), home of Royal Naval Reserve Merseyside,
  Royal Marines Reserve Merseyside and Liverpool URNU since 1995
* USS ''Eaglet'' (SP-909), later YP-909, a United States Navy patrol boat in
  commission from 1917 to 1921

;Aircraft
* P92 Eaglet, a high-winged, light aircraft built by the Tecnam aircraft company

;Persons
* The Eaglet ({{lang|fr|l'Aiglon}}), nickname for Napoleon II

;Fictional characters
* The Eaglet, a character from Alice's Adventures in Wonderland by Lewis Carroll
* Isis Eaglet, also known as Isis Egret, a character in Magical Chronicle
  Lyrical Nanoha Force
